## RedemptionDetails.actualNECTAmount property

Amount of NECT that was actually redeemed by the transaction.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
actualNECTAmount: Decimal;
```

## Remarks

This can end up being lower than `attemptedNECTAmount` due to interference from another transaction that modifies the list of Troves.
